    <h4>NEUROLOGICAL EXAMINATION</h4>
    <h3>Sensory System:</h3>
    <p><em>Modalities: Fine Touch (Cotton Wool), Pain (Neuro Pin), Vibration
        (128Hz Tuning Fork), Proprioception (Joint Position Sense).</em></p>
    <p><em>Key: N = Normal (Intact), R = Reduced, A = Absent. (Compare side to
        side, and distal to proximal).</em></p>
