    <h3>Motor System:</h3>
    <p><em>Inspect for Bulk (Wasting/Hypertrophy) and Tone (Normal, Hypo-,
        Hyper- (Spasticity/Rigidity)).</em></p>
    <table style="width:100%; border-collapse: collapse;" border="1">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Aspect</th>
          <th>Test (Video Time)</th>
          <th>Left</th>
          <th>Right</th>
